","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似冇得整走(?)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上年一個月瘦咗4,5kg搞到大髀內側都有幾條</blockquote><br />\n我上網睇好多資料<br />\nd人話用果酸同a酸會有用<br />\n但唔知邊度買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nA酸唔係for暗瘡咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果酸我用過，不過係做護膚品搽面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係用完對d暗瘡印同疤都冇乜幫助，所以我諗對生長紋都應該冇乜用，用喺身嘅效果應該同你用磨砂差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係用Neostrata嘅gel plus，樓主有興趣可以去萬寧睇下，100mL好似係大約$260"},{"pid":"05b5f2bff110e198e44524b5f4c39e1a6404a43c","tid":227890,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似冇得整走(?)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上年一個月瘦咗4,5kg搞到大髀內側都有幾條</blockquote><br />\n我上網睇好多資料<br />\nd人話用果酸同a酸會有用<br />\n但唔知邊度買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nA酸唔係for暗瘡咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果酸我用過，不過係做護膚品搽面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係用完對d暗瘡印同疤都冇乜幫助，所以我諗對生長紋都應該冇乜用，用喺身嘅效果應該同你用磨砂差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係用Neostrata嘅gel plus，樓主有興趣可以去萬寧睇下，100mL好似係大約$260</blockquote><br />\n我岩岩訂左Neostrata既lotion plus試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望有用<br />\n我係外國d網見到有人話果酸+A酸有用<br />\n而家真係咩都要試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12e20863935f723cdcd2f3a462bc4cf7c32f992","tid":227890,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T15:05:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌我都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要係肚位 搞到好似橙皮紋咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 從來無肥過</blockquote><br />\n有</bloc